These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, sudoku, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, train, tram
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the train is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage    | traveling | writing | sudoku   |
| Transport   | train         | tram   | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, green, white
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, thriller
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person who likes ivory is not the person watching thriller movies##6
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3     |
| Food          | ivory    | white  | green     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | family | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, mystery
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, coffee
1. the person watching epic movies is not the person drinking tea##6
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | mystery | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | fanta | tea   | coffee     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, rock
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, handball
1. the fan reggae is not the person who's sport is handball##6
2. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan reggae##5
3. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | dubstep | rock      |
| Nationality   | ice-hockey | handball  | swimming |

