.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, nigerian, russian
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the turkish##2
3. the person drinking 7up is not the nigerian##6
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the russian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | 7up       | iced-tea |
| Food       | turkish   | russian | nigerian   |

