.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, traveling, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, electrician, accountant
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the accountant is the accountant##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the project-manager##6
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the electrician and the project-manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | traveling | video-games | photography |
| Music-Genre   | electrician     | accountant        | project-manager       |

