2. the person traveling to berlin is not the person watching adventure movies##6
3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | edinburgh     | berlin    | liverpool |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | romance    |

