The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, snowboarding
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
4. the person driving the roller is not the person who's sport is cycling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | roller       | boat | subway  |
| Sport      | snowboarding | cycling  | badminton |

