.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, hot-chocolate
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, snake
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the owner of the goat is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sprite | hot-chocolate   | lemonade |
| Pet           | snake | chinchilla | goat   |

