.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is not the person drinking fanta##6
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsdaffodil##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |   3   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | fanta |
| Job        | daffodil     | bellflower      | rose |

