.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, dahlia
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person who growssunflower##6
4. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food    | sunflower   | dahlia | begonia |
| Hobby   | fishing | collecting | baking |

 